        <span class="tag">About</span>
        <h1>About iRecommendU</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Why we built this site and what we stand for.</p>
        <div class="content">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>iRecommendU exists to cut through the noise. There are thousands of "best of" lists online — most of them written by people who've never actually used the products they're recommending.</p>
          <p>We do things differently. Every tool, SaaS product, or hosting service we review is something we've personally tested or used. Our goal is simple: help you make smarter decisions without wasting money on the wrong product.</p>
          <h2>What We Cover</h2>
          <p>We focus on tech products that matter to builders, creators, and small business owners — web hosting, SaaS tools, productivity apps, ecommerce platforms, and more.</p>
          <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
          <p>We earn a commission when you purchase through our links, at no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the site running. However, our reviews and opinions are never influenced by affiliate relationships — if a product is bad, we'll say so. You can read our full <a href="/disclaimer">affiliate disclosure here</a>.</p>
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>Have a product you'd like us to review? Reach out at <strong>hello@irecommendu.com</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 iRecommendU · <a href="/disclaimer">Affiliate Disclosure</a></p>
    </footer>
